Stop placing the blame where it doesn't belong, and certainly stop expecting a group to take responsibility for someone's INDIVIDUAL remarks on a FLAME BOARD.<br>
<br>
I mean c'mon, are you THAT thin-skinned? This is a FLAME BOARD. Stop holding the guild responsible for what a member says individually in an environment such as this.<br>
<br>
In-game? Sure, be offended and maybe expect something... but here? Jeezus. <br>
